 The Placentia Mustangs 14-and-under team lost to Carolina, Puerto Rico, 2-1, 
in the first round of the Sandy Koufax World Series in Houston. The Mustangs 
will play Decatur, Ga., today in the losers' bracket of the double-elimination 
tournament. Placentia's Jake Pickle gave up three hits in the loss. Tyler 
Sporrer went two for two and Brett Kay had a run-scoring single. 
</P>
