 Eric Stevens, an outfielder from Cypress College and Pacifica High, signed 
with San Jose State, a Cypress College spokesman said. Stevens hit .274 with 
three home runs and 36 RBIs, scored 47 runs, and led the team in walks. Cypress 
won the State championship. 
</P>
