<HEADLINE>
<P>
BASEBALL / DAILY REPORT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Fans holding individual-game tickets bought directly from the Dodgers for 
games that are canceled because of the players' strike must return them to the 
team for a refund. 
</P>
<P>
 Season ticket-holders will be given the choice of a refund or having the money 
applied to the purchase of tickets for postseason games this season or season 
tickets next season. Refunds will be made at the end of each scheduled home 
stand. 
</P>
<P>
 All others should return their tickets to the site of purchase. 
</P>
