<HEADLINE>
<P>
BENEFIT FOR PAWS/LA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A special performance of Dean Farell Bruggeman's play "Show & Tell" will be 
held at the Group Repertory Theatre in North Hollywood on Aug. 18 at 8 p.m. to 
benefit PAWS/LA (Pets Are Wonderful Support), a nonprofit organization in L.A. 
County dedicated to helping people with HIV/AIDS keep their pets. 
</P>
<P>
 Admission is $10 or donation of canned cat or dog food or flea-control 
supplies. Reservations: (818) 769-PLAY. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA081294-0243 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 069327 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
August 12, 1994, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 16; Column 1; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
